{"id": "ChIJ1y8t6F25woARtAIrYszVijs", "rating": 4.2, "userRatingCount": 306, "displayName": {"text": "rōk Coffee and Tea - Olympic Blvd", "languageCode": "en"}, "reviews": [{"name": "places/ChIJ1y8t6F25woARtAIrYszVijs/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25CTE0wdE5TV2g0VTBkRmMyNTNYMmg1WjBWQmNGRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "2 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Nice little spot in Koreatown. You can park in the little attached parking garage for 90 minutes or good luck finding street parking.\n\nDrinks are overpriced as with most spots like this. Matcha was seriously good. I don’t really like matcha but this was the best one I’ve had. Got the matcha duo with oatmilk, black sesame latte with almond milk, and strawberry matcha duo with oat milk. recommend 100% sweet on the matcha.\nStrawberry matcha was kinda gross because it’s just strawberries in syrup, like an ice cream topping.\nBlack sesame latte was okay. Not a fan of the texture of ground up sesame seeds in my latte, but nice flavor if you sip from the top instead of a straw.\n\nMatcha with the foam mixed in is solid. I like it. Gotta be overpriced though with half of a typical coffee cup size filled with ice and charging like 9.25 (+.75 for oat milk or almond milk  options).\nI wanted to try their mugwort options, but it looks like they got rid of those :/\nOn Saturday, there was about 15 people in line around like 4-5pm. Took about 15-30 minutes to order and get our drinks.\nCame back on a Monday around 11am-12pm and there’s no line.\nRestroom was inside of Lasung which was weird but it’s directly connected.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Nice little spot in Koreatown. You can park in the little attached parking garage for 90 minutes or good luck finding street parking.\n\nDrinks are overpriced as with most spots like this. Matcha was seriously good. I don’t really like matcha but this was the best one I’ve had. Got the matcha duo with oatmilk, black sesame latte with almond milk, and strawberry matcha duo with oat milk. recommend 100% sweet on the matcha.\nStrawberry matcha was kinda gross because it’s just strawberries in syrup, like an ice cream topping.\nBlack sesame latte was okay. Not a fan of the texture of ground up sesame seeds in my latte, but nice flavor if you sip from the top instead of a straw.\n\nMatcha with the foam mixed in is solid. I like it. Gotta be overpriced though with half of a typical coffee cup size filled with ice and charging like 9.25 (+.75 for oat milk or almond milk  options).\nI wanted to try their mugwort options, but it looks like they got rid of those :/\nOn Saturday, there was about 15 people in line around like 4-5pm. Took about 15-30 minutes to order and get our drinks.\nCame back on a Monday around 11am-12pm and there’s no line.\nRestroom was inside of Lasung which was weird but it’s directly connected.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Matthew", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/117966759444489266468/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWfi0QfResxTwPO4A9xjavWUEuI9i1WXH2QwH-_fb-W_uFpe2fS=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4"}, "publishTime": "2026-04-28T21:57:52.879818162Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25CTE0wdE5TV2g0VTBkRmMyNTNYMmg1WjBWQmNGRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25CTE0wdE5TV2g0VTBkRmMyNTNYMmg1WjBWQmNGRRAB!2m1!1s0x80c2b95de82d2fd7:0x3b8ad5cc622b02b4"}, {"name": "places/ChIJ1y8t6F25woARtAIrYszVijs/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25WeVJuTndNbFJxU3pFeWFGcERhV1pWYVVWb2FIYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "2 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Come before the lunch rush hour because the cafe fills up pretty quickly. Parking can be tough considering it’s only street parking available. I ordered the matcha duo. It was delicious, I can see why it is the most popular option. I also ordered the matcha Dubai mochi, it was more of a novelty for me and it left my mouth VERY GREEN. That being said, it’s cute for photos. There is also a camera set up, you get a print out and a QR code to access the photo online.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Come before the lunch rush hour because the cafe fills up pretty quickly. Parking can be tough considering it’s only street parking available. I ordered the matcha duo. It was delicious, I can see why it is the most popular option. I also ordered the matcha Dubai mochi, it was more of a novelty for me and it left my mouth VERY GREEN. That being said, it’s cute for photos. There is also a camera set up, you get a print out and a QR code to access the photo online.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Kristina Meza", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/112935054581255414034/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK448eULYIfy8y0SpTfB19YQBQy-bMma6HumhnfY6CwTp5a30oM=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba3"}, "publishTime": "2026-04-28T13:57:47.213456271Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25WeVJuTndNbFJxU3pFeWFGcERhV1pWYVVWb2FIYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25WeVJuTndNbFJxU3pFeWFGcERhV1pWYVVWb2FIYxAB!2m1!1s0x80c2b95de82d2fd7:0x3b8ad5cc622b02b4"}, {"name": "places/ChIJ1y8t6F25woARtAIrYszVijs/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xWSmNXdGZlVkl4ZEhKRFNtdEJaelEyV25ObGNuYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "4 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "On a cold Monday evening, my partner and I had just arrived in LA. We needed a good matcha pick me up, so what better than the number one ranked matcha on Beli. We got the strawberry shortcake matcha and a regular matcha latte. Both were great and had a lot of strong matcha flavor. The strawberry shortcake also actually tasted like strawberry shortcake which blew me away. The portions were a little small, but this place serves quality matcha.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "On a cold Monday evening, my partner and I had just arrived in LA. We needed a good matcha pick me up, so what better than the number one ranked matcha on Beli. We got the strawberry shortcake matcha and a regular matcha latte. Both were great and had a lot of strong matcha flavor. The strawberry shortcake also actually tasted like strawberry shortcake which blew me away. The portions were a little small, but this place serves quality matcha.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Anthony Giang", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/105654367996726388017/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXyDaxrHkkj1GZvAmraejh9m2_A46SA10585TORJsdD7w8ROBFOPA=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba5"}, "publishTime": "2026-02-26T18:54:55.943192093Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xWSmNXdGZlVkl4ZEhKRFNtdEJaelEyV25ObGNuYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xWSmNXdGZlVkl4ZEhKRFNtdEJaelEyV25ObGNuYxAB!2m1!1s0x80c2b95de82d2fd7:0x3b8ad5cc622b02b4"}, {"name": "places/ChIJ1y8t6F25woARtAIrYszVijs/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21odlVuWnFRelpxTTFnM1ptWkdUa0Z4WW1ObU5XYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "3 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Our first time here and had a great service and delicious drinks: matcha duo and lotus einspanner along  with Dubai matcha cookie; chewy!!  The atmosphere was nice and beautiful inside with cherry blossom tree for photo ops.  5 stars🌟🌟🌟🌟🌟highly recommended.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Our first time here and had a great service and delicious drinks: matcha duo and lotus einspanner along  with Dubai matcha cookie; chewy!!  The atmosphere was nice and beautiful inside with cherry blossom tree for photo ops.  5 stars🌟🌟🌟🌟🌟highly recommended.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Kat N.", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/104869090695460350807/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocItU4ii4F4gn6LRjyzYVGcHtbSuL4Cu9_56rlsfHipLboMKJQ=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba5"}, "publishTime": "2026-04-01T21:15:47.613663631Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21odlVuWnFRelpxTTFnM1ptWkdUa0Z4WW1ObU5XYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21odlVuWnFRelpxTTFnM1ptWkdUa0Z4WW1ObU5XYxAB!2m1!1s0x80c2b95de82d2fd7:0x3b8ad5cc622b02b4"}, {"name": "places/ChIJ1y8t6F25woARtAIrYszVijs/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tSTlRIa3dZbVpXY3kxRE1XRkVObFJMZGxvdE5rRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "2 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Heard so much about this place and finally came in to try myself! Took one of the most popular items Matcha Duo and guys, fell in love with it!! Totally worth all the drive and wait. So delicious! That cloud is something else!\nIt's cute and cozy, with nice vibes inside!\nStreet parking is a possibility, no wifi is a hammer, but matcha is great!\nNew fave spot", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Heard so much about this place and finally came in to try myself! Took one of the most popular items Matcha Duo and guys, fell in love with it!! Totally worth all the drive and wait. So delicious! That cloud is something else!\nIt's cute and cozy, with nice vibes inside!\nStreet parking is a possibility, no wifi is a hammer, but matcha is great!\nNew fave spot", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Maria Obry", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/114326836943556634083/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVOalVauka4W5Nzw4lg1ler7Hsu0chY